summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department and authorizing a revokable permit to the Puget Sound Power and Light Company to install electric cables across the Lake Youngs Tunnel right of way in the vicinity of 140th Avenue Southeast and across the Lake Youngs Bypass LIne 4 right of way in the vicinity of its intersections with 143rd Place Southeast and 151st Avenue Southeast, King County, Washington, and specifying the terms.
